    <item>
      <title>Pancake Simulation</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/projects_cg/pancakesimulation/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/projects_cg/pancakesimulation/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Our final goal is to use a robotic arm to control a spatula and implement an autonomous cooking robot. To achieve this, NVIDIA Omniverse is a good tool to generate diverse video simulations, which are used to train a robotic arm&amp;rsquo;s motion for real-world deployment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In this project, I use Isaac Sim as the physics engine to simulate the process of cooking a pancake. By tuning physical parameters of the batter and pancake, I created a realistic animation that mimics real-world pancake cooking behavior in a kitchen setting.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
